1
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:58,440
I've heard that Consort Chun is very knowledgeable

2
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,180
and well-versed in medicine.

3
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,760
Today,

4
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,240
I've learned a lot.

5
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,680
Thank you, Noble Consort Empress.

6
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,190
I’m flattered.

7
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,480
Let's go.

8
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,720
Director Zhang,

9
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:22,160
can jujube and crystal sugar be added

10
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,960
to the prince's light porridge?

11
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,480
A moment, please.

12
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,440
I will try to find a way.

13
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,250
Thank you for your help.

14
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:33,040
Zhen'er, go with Director Zhang to get the prescription.

15
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:33,720
Yes.

16
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,600
It seems

17
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,120
you are in no mindset

18
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:45,400
of sharing with me the leisure of tea and painting.

19
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,040
Thank you for helping me get out of the fix.

20
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,640
I don't know how to thank you.

21
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,480
After Fourth Prince recovers,

22
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,720
I will go invite you.

23
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,280
I am content

24
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,880
knowing you feel this way.

25
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,200
However,

26
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,480
your kindness

27
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,960
was almost eaten by a wolf.

28
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,490
And you're not angry at all?

29
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,080
As long as Fourth Prince recovers,

30
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,240
I seek nothing more.

31
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,040
Lady,

32
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,840
here is your dinner.

33
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,250
I can smell it's rancid so far away.

34
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,329
This is for human consumption?

35
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,680
Lady,

36
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,360
you've entered the Three North Yards.

37
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,040
If someone delivers food to you,

38
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,720
it’ll be a huge blessing here,

39
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,360
so just be content.

40
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,140
However frustrated I appear,

41
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,490
I am the birth mother of Fourth Prince.

42
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,880
But you treat me this way?

43
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,480
Bring your supervisor to me.

44
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:54,960
If it weren't

45
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,560
for Fourth Prince's account,

46
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,600
you'd have to go and fetch

47
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,930
the cold food yourself.

48
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,580
Suit yourself.

49
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,440
Come back.

50
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,600
Come back to me!

51
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,610
Did you come to enjoy my plight?

52
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,440
Why do you have to torment yourself?

53
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,480
Torment myself?

54
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,080
What right do you have

55
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,010
to say that to me?

56
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,640
You robed me of my son.

57
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,660
From the start, it has been you who did wrong.

58
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,680
Having a birth mother like you,

59
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,280
Fourth Prince can easily be implicated.

60
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:11,440
His Majesty loved his child,

61
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,760
and transferred him to Palace of Receiving Celestial Favor.

62
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,200
If you sincerely want to do him good,

63
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,660
don't cause more trouble.

64
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,080
You think I wanted to?

65
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,440
What Empress?

66
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,560
What Consort Yu?

67
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,960
What huge grievance do I hold against them?

68
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,960
No!

69
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,240
I am just a scapegoat.

70
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,720
You willingly aligned with Noble Consort Gao.

71
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,980
You plotted the scheme

72
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,000
and you willingly acted as her vanguard.

73
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,240
Who can you blame now?

74
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,300
Noble Consort?

75
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,460
When I first entered Prince Bao Mansion,

76
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,760
she was only a concubine.

77
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,720
She was even lower than I was.

78
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,250
But soon after that,

79
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,680
just because her father gained power in the court,

80
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,320
the late Emperor

81
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,720
promoted her as His Majesty’s second wife.

82
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,360
Later, after His Majesty's ascension,

83
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,570
overnight she became a Noble Consort.

84
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,160
Her whole family was promoted to the Xianghuang Banner,

85
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,820
overriding crowds of people.

86
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,640
But what about me?

87
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,640
No love, no favor.

88
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,800
No one to depend on.

89
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,180
It was so hard to give birth to Fourth Prince.

90
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:34,560
And I was only promoted by one grade.

91
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:38,100
Tell me, if I didn't attach myself to her,

92
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,720
how could I protect myself?

93
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,760
How could I protect my son?

94
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,659
Just because I acted as her vanguard,

95
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,880
my father and my brothers

96
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,320
all got promoted.

97
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,560
You had the heart to hurt Yongcheng.

98
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,960
You are too vicious to be a mother.

99
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,040
I have to survive first

100
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,720
so I can take care

101
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,760
of my son!

102
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,140
You don't understand!

103
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,290
His Majesty doesn't understand, either.

104
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,660
He only blames me for being paranoid,

105
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,280
being vicious.

106
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,360
But for Yongcheng,

107
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,000
my son,

108
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,000
I can be

109
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,760
Noble Consort Gao's dog.

110
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,760
Whoever she tells me to bite,

111
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,080
I will bite them.

112
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,480
Even if my bones are shattered into pieces,

113
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,760
I won’t regret it.

114
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,360
Who

115
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:43,680
in this world

116
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,409
would love my son more than I do?

117
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,880
Who?

118
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,000
But you!

119
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,120
It's you!

120
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,840
You robbed me of my son,

121
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,680
and my hope.

122
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,600
I didn't come today

123
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,200
to hear you say these things.

124
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,000
I only want to know,

125
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,300
if it was Noble Consort Gao’s idea

126
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,400
that Prince Yi confided to His Majesty.

127
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,680
I am asking you a question.

128
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,010
Why don't you answer me?

129
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,170
This being the case,

130
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,640
there's nothing I can't say.

131
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,360
Yes.

132
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,890
It was Noble Consort Gao who instructed Prince Yi

133
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,440
to report it to His Majesty.

134
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,240
So my family's demise

135
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,580
was closely linked to Noble Consort Gao?

136
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,440
Wrong.

137
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,720
All is wrong.

138
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,120
Hoifa-Nara clan's demise

139
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:05,480
was your fault, Consort Xian.

140
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:09,400
It was you who put on pretense of being lofty,

141
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:12,060
and rejected Noble Consort Gao's olive branch.

142
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,890
It was you acted strictly to the old rules,

143
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:19,490
and refused to beg for leniency for your father and brother.

144
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:20,960
It was you who was so heatless

145
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:23,000
and caused your mother to kill herself at Gate of Divine Might!

146
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,400
In this Forbidden City,

147
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,160
It’s all your fault.

148
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:28,480
a dog is more decent than you!

149
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,120
Did you do anything for anyone?

150
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:35,640
Our family has broken

151
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,320
because of you!

152
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:44,760
The most regretful thing I did in my life

153
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,400
is to give birth

154
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,600
to an incompetent daughter like you!

155
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,280
Even today.

156
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,760
If Consort Chun hadn’t rescued you,

157
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:59,160
could you have got away so easily?

158
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:05,320
The incompetent will be trampled over.

159
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,760
This is your reason for failure.

160
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,720
I saw the wet nurse

161
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,560
feed meat soup to the child that day.

162
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,960
I already had suspicion.

163
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,120
So

164
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,760
I invited Consort Chun for tea.

165
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,440
Consort Chun is versed in medicine.

166
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,840
Her debunking the incident

167
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,300
is better than my doing it.

168
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,880
Do you comprehend?

169
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,130
Did I do anything wrong?

170
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,240
What apology

171
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,200
do I owe you all?

172
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,200
Why do you all

173
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,400
have to force me?

174
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,640
I must be responsible

175
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,370
for Changshou’s death and my mother’s death.

176
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,560
But others can't escape either.

177
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,640
Those who bullied me. Those who owe me.

178
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,200
I will harvest it back,

179
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,720
one by one.

180
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,020
Your highness,

181
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,580
Your highness,

182
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:40,980
Your highness,

183
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,800
Where did you go, your highness?

184
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,120
I was looking for you everywhere

185
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,520
but found no trace of you.

186
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,600
Are you alright?

187
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,760
I'm fine.

188
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,640
I was just feeling stuffy,

189
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:50,170
so I strolled around alone.

190
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,000
Empress,

191
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,400
your clothing is all wet.

192
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,760
I will help you change.

193
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,720
Empress,

194
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,720
Empress,

195
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,720
what's wrong?

196
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,400
What time is it?

197
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,930
It's only midnight.

198
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,440
Please go on sleeping.

199
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,820
I will be on guard here.

200
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,600
No.

201
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,080
Did you hear the crying?

202
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,800
No.

203
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,040
I’ll go check Fourth Prince.

204
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,800
Empress!

205
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:27,480
Your shoes!

206
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,680
Your shoes, Empress!

207
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,680
What's wrong?

208
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,640
What's wrong?

209
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,680
It’s ok.

210
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,560
Come.

211
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,120
Where are

212
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,080
Fourth Prince's servants?

213
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,000
Where are they?

214
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,180
I will go find them.

215
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,000
No need.

216
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,240
I'll deal with that later.

217
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,240
Get me a basin of water

218
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,970
and get him some clean clothes.

219
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,840
Empress,

220
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,000
put on your shoes first.

221
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,840
- You may catch a cold. - Go.

222
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,480
Go.

223
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,120
Yes.

224
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,720
Come.

225
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,080
Yongcheng,

226
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,280
from now on,

227
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,240
I am your mother.

228
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,800
Are you full?

229
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:04,280
Empress,

230
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:06,810
something happened at the Three North Yards.

231
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,440
Are you full, Yongcheng?

232
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,920
Go get the puzzle ring.

233
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,640
Mother will play it with you.

234
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,280
Consort Xian,

235
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,280
that woman in the Three North Yards

236
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,360
hung herself.

237
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,640
Poor thing.

238
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:23,040
Send some memorial gifts for me.

239
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,680
Empress,

240
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:25,960
she deserves it.

241
00:15:26,040 --> 00:15:27,700
You don't need to care for her.

242
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,540
For the sake of Fourth Prince,

243
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,740
I must put in some consideration.

244
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,160
Shall we eat more?

245
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,440
More?

246
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,240
Yes.

247
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:52,240
I told you to write "forgiveness".

248
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:55,740
But you wrote a hundred pages of "patience".

249
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:56,880
Why?

250
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,240
Forgiveness and patience,

251
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,330
aren't they the same thing?

252
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,200
Forgiveness means understanding.

253
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,860
Patience means hibernating.

254
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,240
Do you think I don't know

255
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,500
what you are thinking?

256
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:12,660
You don't even think you were at fault at all.

257
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,840
In your opinion,

258
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,680
all your waiting

259
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:17,200
is to save up energy.

260
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,320
When the right time comes,

261
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,520
you will give your enemy

262
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:21,600
the final blow.

263
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:26,680
Yingluo,

264
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,040
I’ve taught you so much.

265
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,800
Why can't you understand?

266
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,560
I am a hard stone.

267
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,400
I worried you.

268
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,520
You!

269
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,560
Your Majesty,

270
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,880
about Lady Jin of the three North Yards,

271
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,520
her funeral is finished.

272
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,440
Poor Fourth Prince.

273
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,600
He’s so young

274
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,300
and lost his birth mother.

275
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:58,200
If you are fond of Fourth Prince,

276
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,440
why not

277
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:02,570
bring him to Palace of Eternal Spring and raise him here?

278
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:05,290
I manage the imperial harem

279
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:07,119
and the affairs keep me busy.

280
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,440
Consort Xian is graceful,

281
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,210
well-natured and upright.

282
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:13,000
She is most suitable

283
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,530
for raising Fourth Prince.

284
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:17,680
Furthermore, she just lost her family.

285
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:19,880
Fourth Prince

286
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:22,200
is a consolation to her.

287
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,829
Your Majesty,

288
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,280
I may be too wordy,

289
00:17:27,829 --> 00:17:30,200
but Palace of Eternal Spring is too quiet.

290
