They are not beautiful enough.

582
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,800
Yes.

583
00:34:37,080 --> 00:34:38,610
I was too careless just now.

584
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:39,889
I splattered ink

585
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:41,480
all over Her Majesty.

586
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:48,760
I see.

587
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,800
Your Majesty, you're being too secretive.

588
00:34:53,120 --> 00:34:54,960
Whatever you gift me,

589
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:56,400
I

590
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:57,910
will be happy with it.

591
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,160
Your Majesty,

592
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,840
your clothing is all wet?

593
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:01,680
Thanks to

594
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:03,210
your favorite palace maid.

595
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,200
Yingluo,

596
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,560
why were you so clumsy?

597
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:14,250
Beg forgiveness from His Majesty.

598
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:16,440
Yes.

599
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:20,560
It was my fault.

600
00:35:21,120 --> 00:35:22,720
May Your Majesty forgive me.

601
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,120
Your Majesty,

602
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,040
she was too eager to help,

603
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,620
so she caused trouble.

604
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:36,810
If you have the leisure to be angry,

605
00:35:37,520 --> 00:35:38,920
why not go and change?

606
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,120
Your Majesty.

607
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,720
Who allowed in?

608
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,600
Your Majesty,

609
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:01,960
Her Majesty told me

610
00:36:02,640 --> 00:36:04,300
to make amends for my mistake.

611
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:06,360
No need.

612
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:07,850
Go out and kneel.

613
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:09,800
Yes.

614
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:05,680
Your Majesty,

615
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,440
why were you

616
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:09,320
so angry today?

617
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:13,320
Do you know

618
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:16,520
someone's spreading rumors in the Palace?

619
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,520
Rumors?

620
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:21,320
About what?

621
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:28,080
They say you and Consort Chun,

622
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:31,200
are too close

623
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,660
and that's unfitting.

624
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,480
Your Majesty,

625
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:40,200
did you believe

626
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:42,000
a rumor like that?

627
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,480
When I think about it,

628
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,410
it is indeed absurd.

629
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,840
I believed it too easily.

630
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,890
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

631
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,440
I will investigate

632
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:58,080
who spread it

633
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:01,260
and govern the rules of the Palace properly.

634
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:04,080
But Your Majesty,

635
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:07,010
you need to manage your close attendants too.

636
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,280
Your Majesty,

637
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:10,760
I think Yingluo

638
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,620
was just careless for the moment.

639
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:14,810
That girl is usually very prudent.

640
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,810
And very careful in her chores.

641
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,320
Don't you see something?

642
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:23,800
See what?

643
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:28,200
Earlier she ran into

644
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:29,640
my embrace on purpose.

645
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:32,640
It means what I said before was true.

646
00:38:32,920 --> 00:38:35,250
That palace maid is trying to get promoted

647
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,480
relying on her little bit of beauty.

648
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,090
Trying to get promoted?

649
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:41,960
Your Majesty,

650
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:42,760
I know

651
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:44,000
this girl very well,

652
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:46,020
and I don’t think she’s like that.

653
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:54,730
I saw it with my own eyes.

654
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,600
Could that be wrong?

655
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:58,700
If I have not guessed it wrong,

656
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,360
she was trying to lure me.

657
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:02,440
Or she secretly loves me.

658
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,240
Or she is peacockish.

659
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:05,800
Whatever the reason,

660
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,400
she is clearly a cunning fox.

661
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,740
She’s here to seduce the emperor!

662
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,200
Look at her eyes.

663
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:13,760
Look at her smile.

664
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:14,800
She clearly...

665
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:16,730
Clearly you hold bias against her.

666
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:19,480
Because you misunderstand her,

667
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,080
every action and word of hers

668
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:23,040
are wrongly construed.

669
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,600
Forget it.

670
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,980
I will not argue this with you.

671
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:30,240
But one day,

672
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,160
you will come to know

673
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:32,220
what I said is true.

674
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:33,800
Wei Yingluo

675
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:35,370
wants to behold wealth.

676
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:36,850
She is calculating.

677
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:40,440
You must manage her well.

678
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,520
I got it.

679
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:47,530
Until next time, Your Majesty.

680
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:57,920
Shameless.

681
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,520
Shameless.

682
00:40:07,520 --> 00:40:08,280
Yingluo,

683
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:09,800
you didn't know

684
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,730
what Consort Chun and I were doing.

685
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,770
Why did you rush back to warn us?

686
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,280
Rise and speak.

687
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:17,880
Yes.

688
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,240
I didn't know

689
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,240
what was happening

690
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,800
in the resting hall.

691
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:27,000
But since you shut doors

692
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:28,640
and acted low-key,

693
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:31,340
you didn't want others to know it.

694
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:32,560
So I

695
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,820
wagered my life to come back to alert you.

696
00:40:36,520 --> 00:40:37,720
You knew nothing.

697
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:40,320
But you just guarded me?

698
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:41,880
Your Majesty,

699
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:44,410
you taught me to read and write and be upright.

700
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,560
You are a rare good person.

701
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:50,380
If you don't want to talk about it,

702
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,960
you have your reason.

703
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:53,440
My duty is

704
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,000
secure your secret,

705
00:40:55,200 --> 00:40:56,530
instead of snooping it.

706
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,160
Show it to her.

707
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:18,840
This is…?

708
00:41:20,080 --> 00:41:22,080
Since I gave birth to Second Prince,

709
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:25,090
the coldness in me has been spreading.

710
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:27,080
And since this winter,

711
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,530
it’s been getting more severe.

712
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:32,520
Every night, the pain pierces into my bones

713
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:34,280
and I am unable to fall asleep.

714
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:36,000
I’ll sweat all over.

715
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,360
I need to change

716
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:40,360
every hour.

717
00:41:41,640 --> 00:41:42,560
So

718
00:41:43,680 --> 00:41:44,880
Her Majesty invited me

719
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,740
to treat her by acupuncture here.

720
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:49,000
This matter isn't good for others to know,

721
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,120
but I didn't expect…

722
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:52,050
Didn’t expect people in the Palace

723
00:41:52,520 --> 00:41:54,160
could be spreading such rumors

724
00:41:54,160 --> 00:41:55,520
because of it.

725
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:57,920
It's absurd.

726
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:00,680
If His Majesty had burst in

727
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:03,050
and discovered our secret treatment,

728
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,330
the consequence

729
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:05,920
can't be imagined.

730
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:09,760
The women of the harem are valued by their heirs.

731
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,160
Think about it.

732
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:15,260
How could a woman weak to her bones

733
00:42:15,680 --> 00:42:17,360
have children?

734
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:20,360
How can she manage the whole Palace?

735
00:42:21,520 --> 00:42:22,720
So I don’t want

736
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:25,530
to trouble the Imperial Hospital.

737
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:28,290
I could only ask Consort Chun for help.

738
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:30,440
Yingluo,

739
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,920
from now on,

740
00:42:32,400 --> 00:42:33,720
you and Erqing

741
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,320
will help me

742
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:37,040
guard Palace of Eternal Spring.

743
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:37,800
Yes.
